A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Dr. Jeffery D. Cooper and Cooper Pediatrics; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Dr. Jeffery D. Cooper has long been recognized by the citizens of this state for
4 the vital role that he has played in leadership and his deep personal commitment to the
5 welfare of the citizens of Georgia; and
6 WHEREAS, he has diligently and conscientiously devoted innumerable hours of his time,
7 talents, and energy toward the betterment of his community and state as evidenced
8 dramatically by his superlative service as a pediatrician and educator; and
9 WHEREAS, Dr. Cooper's significant organizational and leadership talents, remarkable
10 patience and diplomacy, keen sense of vision, and sensitivity to the needs of the citizens of
11 this state have earned him the respect and admiration of his colleagues and associates; and
12 WHEREAS, his dedicated, compassionate, and innovative work has been recognized through
13 numerous awards, including being named the Best Pediatric Practice Atlanta, by Atlanta
14 BestSelf Magazine, in 2020; earning the Nicholas E. Davies Award for Excellence in Primary
15 Care; and being Voted Best of Gwinnett from 2021 to 2024, by Gwinnett Magazine; and
